00000000                            10  ; Description:
00000000                            11  ; This project is a text-based adventure game written in
00000000                            12  ; Motorola 68000 assembly language using Easy68K.
00000000                            13  ; The player chooses a character (Growler or Stray) and
00000000                            14  ; progresses through seven days of story events.
00000000                            15  ; Each day the player can explore, rest, prepare or inspect
00000000                            16  ; their status. Random events affect health, bravery and
00000000                            17  ; inventory. On the final day the player fights the Lion King
00000000                            18  ; in a boss battle using attack, defend or potion actions.
00000000                            19  ;
00000000                            20  ; Known Bugs / Limitations:
00000000                            21  ; No known critical bugs. Gameplay balance depends on RNG.
00000000                            22  ;-------------------------------------------------------
00000000                            23  
